It's a C# project written specificaly for Microsoft Windows as a favour for a friend of mine.

Description

The application aims at raising productivity at work for those working with Microsoft Access by disabling certain features of Microsoft Windows (e.g. blocking certain keyboard shortcuts and disabling taskbar) and it lets re-enable them by entering the correct password.

To do

